  "text": "All the sperm samples from different species were smeared on Suprasil ® microscope slides (Quartzglas Heinrich QGH, Aachen, Germany) and air dried before evaluation [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . The number of evaluated sperm was as follows: 150 cells for human, 50 for mouse, 60 for monkey and 60 for sea urchin. Overall, more than 1500 spectra were acquired during this study.",
